info.name: lohrasb
info.summary: This versatile tool streamlines hyperparameter optimization in machine learning workflows. It supports a wide range of search methods, from GridSearchCV and RandomizedSearchCV to advanced techniques like OptunaSearchCV, Ray Tune, and Scikit-Learn Tune. Designed to enhance model performance and efficiency, it's suitable for tasks of any scale.
